# Fleet-on-Sepolia booth demo - LOCAL ONLY.
#
# Copy this file to `.env.local` (gitignored) and fill it with a FUNDED
# THROWAWAY key to make the /fleet on-chain toggle anchor real transactions on
# Arbitrum Sepolia (verifiable on Arbiscan).
#
# IMPORTANT: NEXT_PUBLIC_* is inlined into the client bundle at build time. This
# key must therefore be a burner only, and must NEVER be set in the public
# Netlify environment - its absence there is exactly what keeps the hosted site
# in simulation (see resolveSepoliaConfig in lib/sepoliaChain.ts).
#
# A 32-byte hex private key for a burner funded with Arbitrum Sepolia ETH:
NEXT_PUBLIC_FLEET_BURNER_KEY=0xyour_funded_throwaway_key
